NETWORKING 

WHY  NETWORKING ?
	>  FOUNDATION OF ALL THE ATTACKS AND DEFENSE 
	> NETWORK VISIBILITY 
	> EFFECTIVE INCIDENT RESPONSE 
	> REAL WORLD EXPLOIT DEPEND ON IT 
                                                    
HISTORY
	
	>ARPANET => WORLD FIRST NETWORK , BY US MILITARY 


 TYPES OF NETWORK 
	
	> LAN => LOCAL AREA NETWORK 
	> MAN => METRO AREA NETWORK ( LIKE THROUGH CELL 	TOWER )
	>PAN => PERSONAL AREA NETWORK (OUR PERSONAL TS 	OR DEVICE )
	> WAN => WIDE AREA NETWORK (CONNECT WHOLE 	WORLD )


DATA TRANSFER TERMS 
	> LATENCY => HOW FAST THE DATA TRAVEL FROM ONE 	POINT TO ANOTHER 
	> BANDWIDTH => HOW MUCH DATA TRAVEL IN A SECOND 
	> THROUGHPUT =>ACTUAL SPEED OF THE INTERNET 
	> JITTER => MOOD SWINGS OF NETWORK OF FLUCTUATION

