IP ADDRESSING AND SUBNETTING 
	> IPv4 
	> IPv6

TYPES OF IP 
	> PRIVATE IP => THE ADDRESS THAT THE ROUTER GAVE 	TO 	ME , SO THAT I CAN COMMUNICATE WITH THE 	ROUTER 
	> PUBLIC IP => SO THIS IS THE IP THAT MY ISP GIVE TO ME 	SO THAT I CAN COMMUNICATE WITH OUTSIDE WORLD I.E 	YOUTUBE, GOOGLE AND ALL .
	> DYNAMIC IP => SO THE IP ADDRESS WHICH CAN BE 	CHANGED ,WHEN RE CONNECT TO ROUTER 
	> STATIC IP =>  IP THAT NEVER CHANGED , LIKE EVERY 	WEBSITE HAVE ITS PERMANENT IP ADDRESS
